OL,3,CResidents return to homes after south
OL,4,CBelfast security alert
OL,6,FA security alert in south Belfast has
OL,7,Fnow ended.
OL,9,FPolice were called to the Roosevelt
OL,10,FStreet area in the early hours of
OL,11,FThursday morning.
OL,13,FA man and woman, both aged 37, were
OL,14,Farrested on suspicion of drugs-related
OL,15,Foffences.
OL,17,FA number of items discovered were
OL,18,Ftaken away for further forensic
OL,19,Fexaminations.
