OL,3,CResidents return to homes after south
OL,4,CBelfast security alert
OL,6,FSouth Belfast Area Commander Chief
OL,7,FInspector Loreen Glenn said: "Shortly
OL,8,Fbefore 00:10am, a search was conducted
OL,9,Fby police following an earlier arrest
OL,10,Fof a man on suspicion of drugs related
OL,11,Foffences.
OL,13,F"Officers attended the property at the
OL,14,FRoosevelt Street area and a number of
OL,15,Fitems were discovered and have now
OL,16,Fbeen taken away for further forensic
OL,17,Fexaminations.
OL,26,@oD@^OU
