OL,3,CResidents return to homes after south
OL,4,CBelfast security alert
OL,6,F"A public safety operation was
OL,7,Fcommenced and a number of properties
OL,8,Fin the Roosevelt Street and Iverna
OL,9,FStreet areas of south Belfast were
OL,10,Fevacuated.
OL,12,F"Cordons were put in place and the
OL,13,FSandy Row Community Centre was opened
OL,14,Ffor local residents.
OL,16,F"The items were removed by specialist
OL,17,Fofficers for further examination and
OL,18,Fwe would thank the local community for
OL,19,Ftheir understanding and patience
OL,20,Fduring this time, who were able to
OL,21,Freturn to their homes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
